The paper focuses on learning spatio-temporal features in videos using deep convolutional networks and recurrent neural networks. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of gated recurrent unit (GRU) networks, which falls under the sub-category cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper addresses tasks such as human action recognition and video captioning, which are related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI), multimedia (cs.MM), and natural language processing (cs.CL).
